2.FSM Diagram

3.Test Cases
Testing Regular Quick filter

Test Case ID
01
Type of Test
Blackbox
Path Tested
S1 → S2  → S1
Purpose
Testing the basic quick filter feature
Prerequisite 
Freeplane installed and running.
Input Data
A mindmap with several nodes used for filtering and searching
Word used for filtering
Steps
Run Freeplane with a already selected/made mindmap (S1)
Enter word “...” in search bar and click quick filter button (S12)
Check map has been folded into a version that only shows matching nodes with filters.
Click quick filter button, again to exit filter (S21)
Validate map is returned to original unfolded form.

Testing ‘and filter’

Test Case ID
02
Type of Test
Blackbox
Path Tested
S1 → S3  → S1
Purpose
Testing the ‘and filter’ feature
Prerequisite 
Freeplane installed and running.
Input Data
A mindmap with several nodes used for filtering and searching
Word used for filtering
Steps
Run Freeplane with a already selected/made mindmap (S1)
Enter word “...” in search bar and click and filter button (S13)
Check map has been folded into a version that only shows matching nodes with ‘and’ filters.
Click quick filter button to exit filter (S31)
Validate map is returned to original unfolded form.

Testing ‘or filter’

Test Case ID
03
Type of Test
Blackbox
Path Tested 
